{"tid":2213392,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論]ONEPIECE 海賊王 ワンピース 991漫畫中文情報,圖","createTime":"2020-09-22T13:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T03:08:51.000Z","uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7230a79b7e71f2d7864103240ba735e2f99ad536","tid":2213392,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9JECNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9JECNs.jpg&h=4ab3ee96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5vSXNt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5vSXNt.jpg&h=862aa6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n991話標題「讓我（們）死」（不確定）<br />\n路飛接受德雷克加入同盟，不過索隆、甚平跟弗蘭奇不樂意。<br />\n德雷克被索隆阻止的時候阿普出現，並攻擊了索隆和德雷克，他們兩人聯手一起打阿普。<br />\n佩吉萬跟烏爾緹攻擊草帽團，但被烏索普和娜美吸引了注意力。<br />\n月獅貓狗打倒了傑克。凱多出現。<br />\n凱多向赤鞘武士發出熱息，被錦衛門用狐火劍術擋下。<br />\n最後，錦衛門最後作為御田的武士喊出「讓我（們）死」的台詞（即本話標題）<br />\n下週不休刊。"},{"pid":"58d5c3e1d14d584ff16bec3f079efe2b4b483765","tid":2213392,"uid":2857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">請問遠阪凜(狗隻#3020)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149465\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc0f1d8d0c46bdbc89821c76000fd28d81c447d4","tid":2213392,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"5毛 遠阪凜#3020 手持至少6個連登帳號,請admin跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n熱烈恭賀牙井當選區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1751830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1751830</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好回覆呢個post，唔好幫佢賺錢！<br />\n會員#3020遠阪凜係連登知名過街老鼠及5毛！<br />\n牽涉多單竊取會員資料，宣傳特定網頁！<br />\n多次洗版式帶風向